          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>End Pensions in Congress Act or the EPIC Act</b></p> <p>This bill excludes future Members of Congress from the Federal Employees Retirement System (FERS) and requires Members currently enrolled in FERS or the Civil Service Retirement System to opt in to continue their enrollment.</p>]]></text>
